longBusinessSummary: Fashionette AG operates an online platform for premium and luxury fashion accessories. The company provides handbags, shoes, sunglasses, watches, and jewelry. It operates in Germany, Austria, Switzerland, France, Italy, the Netherlands, Sweden, and the United Kingdom. The company was founded in 2008 and is based in Dusseldorf, Germany.
